<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bḥbk ạlsạmy lqd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biḥubĩka ạlsãạmī laqad̊
 nazal̊ta min̊ ạảʿ̊lay̱ ạlsãmā
 ạảkẖ̊laẙta naf̊saka waqad̊
 ạảẓ̊har̊ta ḥubaⁿ̃ạ qad̊ samā

[V2]
 2- biḥubĩka ạlsãạmī lanā
 qad̊ ṣir̊ta ʿab̊daⁿạ yā qadīr̊
 ʿab̊daⁿạ muṭīʿaⁿạ kāmilạaⁿ
 yā kẖaẙra mal̊jā wanaṣīr̊

[V3]
 3- biḥubĩka ạlsãạmī laqad̊
 qum̊ta maqāmanā ạlạảtẖīm̊
 lidẖā ḥamal̊ta ại̹tẖ̊manā
 ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlībi yā raḥīm̊

[V4]
 4- biḥubĩka ạlsãạmī laqad̊
 nil̊nā ạl̊ḥayāẗa lilạảbad̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ mutã ʿanãạ ṭāyỉʿaⁿạ
 litaf̊tadīnā yā ṣamad̊

[V5]
 5- biḥubĩka ạlsãạmī laqad̊
 wuhib̊nā kulã ạl̊barakāt̊
 lakinã sẖakẖ̊ṣaka lanā
 ạảtẖ̊manu min̊ kulĩ ạl̊hibāt̊

[V6]
 6- fālsẖũk̊ra nuh̊dīka ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 wāl̊ḥam̊da ạảẙḍaⁿạ wālsũjūd̊
 liḥubĩka ạlsãạmī ạlãdẖī
 ạảj̊zal̊ta lanā yā wadūd̊</lyrics>
<author>trnymạt rwḥyẗ 95</author>
</song>